### Регистрация нового пользователя
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser3",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test3@mail.ru"
}

### Вход в систему
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser3",
  "password": "123456"
}